The paper deals with an online optimization problem in the context of sensor networks, which involves graph theory, game theory, and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), followed by cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
